---
title: Veggie Red Thai Style Noodle Soup with Soy Mushrooms, Baby Corn and Green Beans
description: Red chillies give Thai Red its signature colour, as well as its flavour and heat! Here, our Veggie Red Thai Style Noodle Soup is loaded with veg and egg noodles in a curried coconut milk base.
